data.title: Notes of Lady Polwarth concerning the movements of Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham in South America, 1873-1876, and of Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham and Gabrielle Cunninghame Graham in Texas, Me
data.text:
Notes of Lady Polwarth concerning the movements of Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham in South America, 1873-1876, and of Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham and Gabrielle Cunninghame Graham in Texas, Mexico and Spain, 1880-1883., 1873-1883., Acc.11335/158. Correspondence, notes, literary papers and other papers of the Cunninghame Graham family, mostly of Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham; and financial and administrative papers relating to Gartmore and Ardoch., Acc.11335/1-227. National Library of Scotland Archives and Manuscripts Division.
